title: World of One v1 3-HI2U
description:
World of One v1.3.1 (c) Grimwood Team

Release 23/09/2017

Protection: Steam
Game Size: 1 DISC

Game Type: Action, Adventure, Indie [RELEASE NOTES]

You are about to get on a journey around small planet-like
worlds as if you were in the Little Prince's world. However
these ones are filled with monsters that are striving to kill
you, deadly traps and riddles, which require you to be
quick-witted and attentive

We are glad to tell you about the release of a new version of
the game. Plenty of exciting changes are waiting for you in this
update. They will make your experience more comfortable and
enhance your sense of immersion into the grim atmosphere
of World of One 

[INSTALL NOTES] 

1 Mount / burn image 2 Install 3 Copy content from 'Crack' folder and replace game dir files 4 Play game 5 If U like it, buy it!
